00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 7=

4
00:01:10,959 --> 00:01:12,120
Miss Shen,

5
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:13,319
you are also named Shen

6
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,920
and are from Chizhou.

7
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,760
Do you happen to know

8
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:18,280
Senior Attendant Rou?

9
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:27,280
Senior Attendant Rou
is my younger concubine-born sister.

10
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:33,319
Greetings, Nanqiao.

11
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,719
Zhinian.

12
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:39,959
Young Master Lu.

13
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,719
Greetings,

14
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,000
Senior Attendant Rou.

15
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,599
Indeed, she has
an extraordinary appearance.

16
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,110
Since we were young,

17
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,990
my sister has always
been prettier than I am.

18
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,120
She is also more ambitious than me.

19
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:57,439
She only chooses
the most outstanding men to marry.

20
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,159
I have misspoken.

21
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,480
What did you do wrong?

22
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,920
When it comes to marriage,

23
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,680
one should follow parents' orders

24
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,840
and the matchmaker's words.

25
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,199
You have done very well.

26
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,439
Shen Zhinian,

27
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:15,479
you must learn to be content.

28
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,240
Follow the palace rules

29
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,639
and serve the Emperor well.

30
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,790
I will follow your teachings,
Dowager Consort.

31
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:23,879
Now that my wishes have come true,

32
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,280
it's all thanks to Nanqiao.

33
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,759
Thank you, Nanqiao.

34
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,120
Zhinian,

35
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,520
we can catch up

36
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,759
on our sisterly bond later.

37
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,120
Emperor,

38
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:37,120
I wish to adopt
Nanqiao as my goddaughter.

39
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,400
What do you think?

40
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,960
(The younger sister entered the palace)

41
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:45,100
(and the elder sister
saved the Dowager Consort.)

42
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,840
(What a perfect collaboration.)

43
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,520
Whatever you say, Dowager Consort.

44
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:50,919
Alright.

45
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,719
Then, you will be granted the title of
County Princess Ning'an,

46
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:57,159
and you will reside in Qingquan Palace.

47
00:02:58,100 --> 00:02:59,860
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

48
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:01,660
- Thank you, Dowager Consort.
- Thank you, Dowager Consort.

49
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,560
(I never expected)

50
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:05,960
(that Shen Nanqiao
would dare to enter the palace.)

51
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,250
The Dowager Consort was
originally going to Mount Ling,

52
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,960
but she changed her route
to Nanhua Temple midway.

53
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,919
Shen Nanqiao came to
the capital from Chizhou.

54
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:17,680
On the way, there is Babao Temple,

55
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,200
which is most popular with civilians,

56
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,599
but she didn't go there.

57
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,479
Instead, she took a detour
to Nanhua Temple.

58
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:25,120
Was it a coincidence,

59
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:26,439
or was it intentional?

60
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:29,479
I think these two sisters
are both very suspicious.

61
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,800
Keep a close eye on them.

62
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:32,960
Find out the truth.

63
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,680
Yes, Your Majesty.

64
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,840
(Tinglan Palace)

65
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,800
County Princess Ning'an has arrived!

66
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,719
So, you live in such a remote place.

67
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,840
Life here must be
very difficult for you.

68
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,879
It's still better than being at home.

69
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,060
After all, this is the palace.

70
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,199
Otherwise,

71
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:53,080
you wouldn't have followed me here.

72
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,400
There's no need to pretend.

73
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,919
Without power or influence,

74
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:01,759
you are less than an ant in this palace.

75
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:04,159
I am different.

76
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:06,110
Lu has come to
the capital for the re-examination.

77
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,240
He will surely pass.

78
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,700
When he becomes the top scholar,

79
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:10,240
I will be both a County Princess

80
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,840
and the top scholar's wife.

81
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:14,840
We both come from the Shen family.

82
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,040
We are tied together.

83
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,560
If you live well,

84
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,100
it's good for the Shen family and me.

85
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,600
You want to benefit from me?

86
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:21,839
Likewise,

87
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:23,519
if you make a mistake,

88
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,200
it will implicate the whole Shen family.

89
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,399
I hope you think clearly

90
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,920
before you do anything.

91
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:30,199
What do you mean?

92
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,519
I'm busy.

93
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,480
County Princess Ning'an,
Young Master Lu,

94
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,480
please leave.

95
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,800
Let's go.

96
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:42,360
My father-in-law
asked me to give this to you.

97
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,240
Don't be afraid.

98
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:44,560
Lu,

99
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,360
let's go.

100
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:50,360
Stop pretending to be so devoted.

101
00:04:50,490 --> 00:04:52,519
He turned around and
married Shen Nanqiao anyway.

102
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:54,270
If he were truly noble,
he shouldn't have married anyone.

103
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:56,319
(Lu Jianglin's loss of composure today)

104
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:58,100
(must have been noticed
by someone with intent.)

105
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,560
(I must be extra careful.)

106
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,759
County Princess Ning'an
came from Chizhou.

107
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,500
She should have
taken the Xu County route.

108
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,560
Why would she take
a detour to Mount Wei?

109
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:29,720
(Why does he look even more terrifying
than in my past life?)

110
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:37,399
I went to Nanhua Temple
to pray for my husband,

111
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:38,950
hoping he would pass the imperial exam.

112
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:42,279
Nanqiao is gentle and virtuous.

113
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:46,399
It's just a pity
that such a beautiful flower

114
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,720
has fallen into an ordinary family.

115
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,839
You are too kind, Dowager Consort.

116
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:53,279
I am merely of humble appearance.

117
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:55,800
I cannot compare to Zhinian's beauty.

118
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,959
I heard from Nanqiao's maid

119
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:00,279
that Nanqiao was originally
the one to enter the palace.

120
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:02,360
It was Shen Zhinian who made a scene,

121
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,720
insisting on breaking
the engagement with Lu Jianglin

122
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,480
because she wanted to become a consort.

123
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:08,480
Nanqiao felt

124
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,879
indebted to Jianglin,

125
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,079
which is why she
was willing to marry him.

126
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:13,560
Your Majesty,

127
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,319
Shen Zhinian

128
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,680
is no saint.

129
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:21,680
Your Majesty,

130
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,680
my sister's love for wealth and status

131
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,199
is not exactly a sin.

132
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,839
Mm.

133
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,600
County Princess, you're right.

134
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:31,519
It's not a crime for a woman

135
00:06:31,530 --> 00:06:32,439
to seek a good husband.

136
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,560
Your Majesty,

137
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,600
have you taken a liking to Shen Zhinian?

138
00:06:37,330 --> 00:06:39,180
The County Princess
saved your life, Dowager Consort.

139
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:41,360
So, I cannot mistreat her family.

140
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,319
I will grant Shen Zhinian the title

141
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:45,600
of Lady of Beauty

142
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,800
to demonstrate your virtue,
Dowager Consort.

143
00:06:48,079 --> 00:06:50,079
A promotion of four ranks without merit?

144
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,759
That is improper.

145
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,000
What do you think, County Princess?

146
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:59,360
There is no need for such

147
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,240
generosity.

148
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:09,720
I heard you once had
an engagement with Lu Jianglin.

149
00:07:14,550 --> 00:07:16,199
Looking at your expression,
Your Majesty,

150
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:17,800
could I be so bold

151
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,480
as to think you are jealous?

152
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:21,399
Me, jealous?

153
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:24,160
You think too highly of yourself, no?

154
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,360
I've always been broad-minded,

155
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:27,860
so I love thinking highly of myself.

156
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:29,959
I didn't like the poor scholar
my father chose.

157
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,900
I only love a majestic man
like Your Majesty.

158
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,879
What a blatant gold-digger.

159
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,519
In this world,

160
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:39,360
which woman wouldn't want her husband

161
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,480
to be handsome, brave,

162
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,480
talented, and capable?

163
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,000
This mouth of yours

164
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,240
is indeed your greatest talent.

165
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:51,759
So, do you like it, Your Majesty?

166
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:52,959
I don't.

167
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:58,199
But I love Your Majesty's mouth.

168
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:02,079
Your Majesty's mouth is stubborn.

169
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,560
How thick-skinned.

170
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:11,720
I am only thick-skinned
for Your Majesty.

171
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,760
I would never be
this way with anyone else.

172
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:14,959
Because Your Majesty

173
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,639
is the finest man in the world.

174
00:08:17,759 --> 00:08:18,560
Shen Zhinian,

175
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:20,759
you'd better

176
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:23,199
have never said
these words to another man.

177
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,519
I swear,

178
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:27,439
I have only said them to you.

179
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:31,260
♪Dim lamps, concerns unheard by anyone♪

180
00:08:32,180 --> 00:08:37,740
♪All the spring colors
lean toward one person♪

181
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:41,480
Do you realize that deceiving
the Emperor is a capital offense?

182
00:08:42,620 --> 00:08:45,980
♪Every step is treacherous,
regardless of the world♪

183
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:49,980
♪Flowers wither easily,
but obsession remains♪

184
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:52,759
I may love to joke,

185
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,840
but one thing is true.

186
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:58,679
I really like you very much, Your Majesty.

187
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,440
Shen Zhinian,

188
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:08,240
you'd better be able
to keep up this act forever.

189
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:12,860
♪I don't ask for equality,
only that you hear me♪

190
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:16,380
♪Years of longing haunt
the palace gates, too deep to hide♪

191
00:09:16,380 --> 00:09:19,820
♪I endured the years,
guarding a single truth♪

192
00:09:19,820 --> 00:09:23,260
♪Spending my youth on deep love,
asking not of right or wrong♪

193
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:26,340
♪Though rumors cover the bed,
my heart is sincere♪

194
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:31,660
♪Only wishing to stay by your side,
never betraying this bond of fate♪

195
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:41,480
The Emperor has visited twice
but hasn't stayed the night.

196
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:43,240
Could he really have
some hidden ailment?

197
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,600
It doesn't seem like it.

198
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,080
I don't understand why either.

199
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:11,399
Every time it reaches
a critical moment, he stops.

200
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,039
Perhaps,

201
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,600
he still doesn't trust me.

202
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:19,159
Young Lady, why did you tell His Majesty

203
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:21,000
about your marriage to Lu Jianglin?

204
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:23,799
My marriage to him isn't a secret.

205
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:25,500
His Majesty would
find out sooner or later.

206
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,890
It's better that I tell him myself.

207
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,960
But what if His Majesty really thinks

208
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:31,280
you're someone who favors
the rich and disdains the poor?

209
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:34,799
Since it's His Majesty's wealth
that I love,

210
00:10:35,759 --> 00:10:37,279
he will only be happy.

211
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,759
It's a man's nature to enjoy conquest.

212
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,879
Senior Attendant, a pigeon just flew in.

213
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,840
Isn't this Lu Jianglin's pigeon?

214
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,480
Drive it away.

215
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,039
Yes.

216
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,480
Lu Jianglin is so indiscreet.

217
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,399
It will cause trouble.

218
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,799
I must find a way

219
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,080
to send him away.

220
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,120
Could it really be as Nanqiao said

221
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:09,559
that she favors the rich
and disdains the poor,

222
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,960
so she abandoned me?

223
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:19,440
Shen Zhinian,

224
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:22,279
I treated you with sincerity.

225
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:24,720
How could you betray me?

226
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:28,220
(Tinglan Palace)

227
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,639
Young Lady,
why do you use a bell to catch insects?

228
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:33,960
This is an insect-catching bell.

229
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:36,600
Its sound can trick the insects

230
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:38,679
into thinking
it's a female's mating call.

231
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:41,970
Can this really attract the insects
the little white snake likes to eat?

232
00:11:42,690 --> 00:11:44,480
I looked through
ancient records last night.

233
00:11:44,639 --> 00:11:46,399
The insects the little white snake likes

234
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,559
are unique on Mount Tian.

235
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:49,790
Since it's hiding in the Tinglan Palace
and won't leave,

236
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,080
it means there must be

237
00:11:51,159 --> 00:11:52,919
the insects it likes here.

238
00:11:53,799 --> 00:11:56,320
If you help His Majesty raise the snake,
he will be happy.

239
00:11:56,799 --> 00:11:58,399
Whether he's happy is one thing,

240
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,039
but the little white snake
will be happy.

241
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:03,399
If I can't win His Majesty's favor,

242
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:05,080
I'll just kidnap the little white snake.

243
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,480
Selling it for money
would also sustain me.

244
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:10,080
Come give me the cage.

245
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,120
Your hand...

246
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,559
Why are you here again?

247
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:23,279
Hadn't I come, you would have
kidnapped my little white snake

248
00:12:23,279 --> 00:12:24,230
without me even knowing.

249
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:27,480
It's raising, not kidnapping.

250
00:12:27,660 --> 00:12:29,000
Doesn't Your Majesty want to know

251
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,679
what the little white snake
likes to eat?

252
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:33,519
You should be glad
it doesn't like to eat you.

253
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:35,600
Otherwise, I would have to kill you

254
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,600
and feed it with your blood.

255
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,759
If it really wanted to eat me,

256
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:47,000
would Your Majesty

257
00:12:47,399 --> 00:12:48,720
really kill me?

258
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:04,800
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

259
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:11,760
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

260
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:15,760
♪If we don't meet♪

261
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:19,200
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

262
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:25,920
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

263
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:32,720
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

264
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:39,400
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

265
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:46,600
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

266
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:53,480
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

267
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:59,600
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

268
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:07,120
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

269
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:13,960
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

270
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:20,680
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

